.TH SM-NEW 1  "new " 
.SH NAME
new \- Create a new workspace, client, project, engagement, or template
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBnew\fR [\fB\-h\fR|\fB\-\-help\fR] [\fIPATH\fR] 
.SH DESCRIPTION
Create a new workspace, client, project, engagement, or template
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
Print help
.TP
[\fIPATH\fR]
Path or name (no args = workspace, absolute path = workspace, single name = client, multi\-segment = hierarchy)
